00:05:08,230 --> 00:05:09,230
Yes.

71
00:05:09,230 --> 00:05:14,030
Then, where was your cell phone at that time?

72
00:05:14,030 --> 00:05:15,430
Here it comes!

73
00:05:17,130 --> 00:05:21,130
