107
00:07:02,430 --> 00:07:04,230
would cooperate in establishing an alibi for the defendant.

108
00:07:05,730 --> 00:07:06,930
But...

109
00:07:09,130 --> 00:07:10,930
Mrs. Masako Kameda.

110
00:07:10,930 --> 00:07:12,830
On the night of the incident,

